# La-ah-ah-ah-ah-ah # 

308
00:12:33,758 --> 00:12:34,758
♪ La-ah... ♪ 

309
00:12:37,762 --> 00:12:39,596
Your range is better.

310
00:12:39,681 --> 00:12:41,765
It was impressive
a year and a half ago,

311
00:12:41,850 --> 00:12:43,767
but it's even
better now.

312
00:12:43,852 --> 00:12:45,686
This is a private rehearsal.

313
00:12:45,753 --> 00:12:48,188
What song are you
auditioning with?

314
00:12:48,256 --> 00:12:50,390
That's none of your business,
okay? If you've come here

315
00:12:50,442 --> 00:12:52,976
to ask me to join your little
group, the answer is no.

316
00:12:53,061 --> 00:12:54,561
My loyalty is
to the New Directions.

317
00:12:54,612 --> 00:12:56,029
They're my family,

318
00:12:56,097 --> 00:12:58,615
and family means something--
at least to me.

319
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:01,985
Rachel, like we talked
about before I'm your
birth mother.

320
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:03,603
Yeah, but not my mother.
I know, okay?

321
00:13:03,655 --> 00:13:05,438
I almost had to go to
therapy because of you.
Rachel...

322
00:13:05,490 --> 00:13:08,041
Look, I-I'll be polite, okay?
Don't worry, if I see you

323
00:13:08,109 --> 00:13:10,610
