00:13:16,918 --> 00:13:18,418
"Somewhere
there's a place for us."

327
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:21,839
I just said that there wasn't.
I'm talking about the song.

328
00:13:21,923 --> 00:13:23,290
I played Maria 18 times.

329
00:13:23,341 --> 00:13:24,925
"Somewhere" is the perfect
audition song for you.

330
00:13:24,976 --> 00:13:25,976
You should do it.

331
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,797
Well, I was considering it.

332
00:13:30,849 --> 00:13:33,016
But it's a very
challenging song so...

333
00:13:33,101 --> 00:13:35,068
I was just going to do
"I Feel Pretty,"

334
00:13:35,136 --> 00:13:36,687
which I'm actually
amazing at.

335
00:13:36,771 --> 00:13:38,939
You will never become
a star or get the lead

336
